{"tid":521510,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[四五千做國家主席] 不如搞panadol藥丸手鏈","createTime":"2018-01-06T15:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T06:42:15.000Z","uid":79353,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dab1b8886470cab053ac688dd919403906a31585","tid":521510,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:29:01.000Z","msg":"話說港女最愛貴價高檔穿玻璃珠手作 PANDORA<br />\n一條咁樣幾粒珠仔，要賣成五千幾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn-tp2.mozu.com/12282-17348/cms/files/998182e0-f838-4360-b900-b06995d76692?_mzcb=_1510271072861\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-tp2.mozu.com%2F12282-17348%2Fcms%2Ffiles%2F998182e0-f838-4360-b900-b06995d76692%3F_mzcb%3D_1510271072861&h=dbb50e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然咁既爛鬼首飾，同細路仔玩穿膠珠冇分別，咁都可以呃到錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如我地又集資出 panadol 藥丸手鏈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺去遊客區藥房診所專呃蝗客，話全部都係正廠出既靚藥，唔會食到大陸假藥，呃返班蝗幾千蚊一條藥鏈，為港爭光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例子圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/91/ab/9e/91ab9ec3b45b615cca01443b0d60620b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F91%2Fab%2F9e%2F91ab9ec3b45b615cca01443b0d60620b.jpg&h=b6cd839a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.choice.com.au/~/media/709febd8857d4e5db42ada00eddd4c49.ashx?jq=80&amp;w=994&amp;h=559\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.choice.com.au%2F~%2Fmedia%2F709febd8857d4e5db42ada00eddd4c49.ashx%3Fjq%3D80%26w%3D994%26h%3D559&h=d04327ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7df547fa7f7d7f0ef92b55fe53c10a0d0b5ba30","tid":521510,"uid":79353,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:39:16.000Z"